\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Get going!\u8221\'94 he shouted}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 .}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  Mandri got going. He took two steps, and when that wasn\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92t hurried enough, Hill}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  shoved him in the back}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  as if that would help. Mandri\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s stiff legs couldn\u8217\'92t cope with the unbalancing and he tumbled forward into Seb\u8217\'92s hips. Seb went sprawling, and so did Mazyd Obo.}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  The three of them tumbled together into the glinting darkness, much}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  yelp}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 ing and groaning split.}
