\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Mandri felt a brush of air as Seb darted back into the cave.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Mandri tried to blink out the burned-in image of day which occluded the world from view}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 .}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  Soon it faded into a color that wasn\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92t the blue of a midday sky as he\u8217\'92d been expecting. He looked up, and there was a circle of blue above him, and when he looked back down at the world around it became clear that he was encircled by tall walls of stone that rose up by a good thirty feet. He was sitting at the bottom of a colossal white limestone bucket, a pit cave, and t}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 he }{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 prenoon s}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 un}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  }{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 angled }{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 it\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s light }{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 down the sides of this bucket, leaving }{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Mandri\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s half of the}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  pit in a dusty, radiant glow, and the other half in a }{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 crescent }{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 shadow which seemed to glow }{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 with warmth from }{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 from all the reflected light}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  bouncing around.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 There were dark figures milling about in this warm shadow, some standing, some sitting against the rock. }{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Self-awareness. He was kneeling like an idiot in a}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  spotlighted}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  splotch of}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  sand, he on one side, the shadow of bandits on the other. He couldn\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92t see their eyes, but he could feel their glares descend upon him. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 One of them stepped forward and into the sunlight\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 a Zosan woman. Her smooth, dark face was framed by }{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 a tight}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  white scarf that was loosely wrapped around }{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 the}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  }{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 neck}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 . The rest of her figure was shrouded to the ankles by a beige }{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 robe}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 . It was a clean and simple look, and despite the wear and tear that spoke of }{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 a }{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 life }{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 roughing it }{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 out in the Sand, the }{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 woman}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  wore it with a hint of regal bearing\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 shoulders }{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 held }{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 in a kind of self-important sw}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 oo}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 p that showed she\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92d }{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 been }{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 trained in the art of woman-standing-still. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Her voice was as imperious }{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 and}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  uncompromising }{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 as her posture}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 . }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93You\u8217\'92re the dead boy,\u8221\'94 she said. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Yes, Mandri was the dead boy. It was such a simple matter of fact, but the way she said it made it seem like it was some keen insight that was obvious only to her. }
