\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Uh, well\u8230\'85\u8221\'94 Should he nod? \u8220\'93I think your other prisoner escaped.\u8221\'94}
