\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Forty}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  turned to }{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 a lounging shadow near the shadow\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s edge.}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Tob, Do you have Papi\u8217\'92s clothes?\u8221\'94}
