\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0  Tucked right inside the bottom swerve of the pit\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s crescent shadow was a burly man stretched out amongst a couple burlap sacks. This man\u8217\'92s head could be best described as a wiry bush of black, for between the beard, brows, and hair there was hardly a splotch of skin. There was a mouth in there somewhere, because sticking out of it was a smoking pipe of freeweed. }
