\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Forty sauntered over to the limestone wall and sat down next to}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  this irascible bush of a }{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 man}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 . \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93This is Tob,\u8221\'94 she said.}
