\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Are those Papi\u8217\'92s clothes?\u8221\'94 }{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 she}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  asked as she pointed to the bundle of clothes }{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 that lay between}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  Tob}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s elbow and armpit.}
