\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Mandri picked up the bundle. He pulled at the plaited hemp string and unrolled the clothes onto the ground. }{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 T}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 here was a thin brown woolen robe that was crumpled with salt and sweat, and }{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 a loose fitting cowl, brown}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 ,}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  }{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 with a diamond pattern of beige sewn down the sides. There was also a pair of rawhide boots that, when he put them on, seemed cut perfectly to size. It was all in good shape, too, though the }{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 robe}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  had a blood stain around the collar and the}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 re was a splotch of blood running along the length of the left arm and all down the left side to the hem}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 .}
